<paragraph blockId="8.[136,1452,158,1085]" pageId="8" pageNumber="295">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[189,473,410,436]" pageId="8" pageNumber="295">Culture characteristics:</emphasis>
—Ascospores germinated on PDA within 24 hours. Colonies on PDA were white when young, became pale brown, dense, but thinning towards the edge, medium dense, white from above, reverse sides were white at the margin, flesh to pale brown at centre, no pigmentation were produced on PDA medium, no conidia were observed on PDA or OA media.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="8.[136,1452,158,1085]" box="[189,1088,554,581]" pageId="8" pageNumber="295">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[189,445,554,580]" pageId="8" pageNumber="295">Habitat/Distribution:</emphasis>
—Known to inhabit dead wood, 
<collectingRegion box="[812,1001,554,580]" country="China" name="Hainan" pageId="8" pageNumber="295">Hainan Province</collectingRegion>
, 
<collectingCountry box="[1013,1084,554,580]" name="China" pageId="8" pageNumber="295">China</collectingCountry>
.
</paragraph>
